data.current_description: Forces a job to run now. When this method is called, Cloud Scheduler will dispatch the job, even if the job is already running.
data.description_suggestion: Forces a job to execute immediately, bypassing the normal schedule. When called, Cloud Scheduler dispatches the job even if it is already running, allowing concurrent executions. Requires the job name in the format 'projects/{project}/locations/{location}/jobs/{job}'. Returns the executed Job object. The job must be in Job.State.ENABLED to run.
